text: Ismail Bilen (born in 25, October 1961 in Mosh in Turkey) is a Turkish lawyer, politician and member of the Turkish Parliament == Biography == He graduated from the Faculty of Law of the University of Istanbul. also worked as an independent lawyer and was a deputy from Manisa Ismail is married and has three children ==References== Category:Turkish politicians Category:1961 births Category:Living people
title: Ismail Bilen
